<h2 style="text-align: center;">Tips for Comfortable Menstrual cycle (Periods)</h2>
[caption id="attachment_1071" align="alignnone" width="500"]<img class="wp-image-1071 size-full" src="http://homemadesolutions.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Comfortable-Menstrual-cycle-Periods2.jpg" alt="Comfortable Menstrual cycle (Periods)" width="500" height="333" /> Menstrual cycle (Periods)[/caption]

&nbsp;
<p style="text-align: justify;">It is a fact that women get a menstrual cycle every month,¬†a woman can not define the pain and irritation in menstrual cramps, mood swings, and bloating, for some difficult time of the month is extremely unbearable. Here we bring to you the most effective ways that will make your periods more comfortable.</p>


[caption id="attachment_1021" align="alignnone" width="500"]<img class="wp-image-1021" src="http://homemadesolutions.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Calcium-Rich-Foods-300x169.jpg" alt="Foods full of Calcium, veg non veg egg green leaves, milk, almonds, ots, panir" width="500" height="281" /> 1. Foods full of Calcium[/caption]
<p style="text-align: justify;">Calcium is one of the best natural supplements that have been conclusively proven to help women in the menstrual cycle. Clinical trials show that calcium can provide relief for almost all the symptoms experienced during a menstrual cycle. studies show that women who eat more foods rich in calcium and vitamin D have lower risks of pain in a Menstrual cycle.</p>


[caption id="attachment_1040" align="alignnone" width="500"]<img class="wp-image-1040" src="http://homemadesolutions.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/DryFoods-2-3.jpg" alt="Dry foods, healthy snacks" width="500" height="267" /> 2. Dry foods, healthy snacks[/caption]
<p style="text-align: justify;">fried and junk foods are harmful to our health,¬†¬†fried and junk¬†foods should definitely be avoided when women are in the menstrual cycle.¬†Adopt healthy eating habits, especially when your body needs extreme care, in menstrual cycle eating healthy and more often as it helps in metabolism. dry foods healthy snacks foods that are high in vitamins, eat fresh vegetables, ¬†nuts, and fruits.</p>


[caption id="attachment_1056" align="alignnone" width="468"]<img class="wp-image-1056" src="http://homemadesolutions.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Heat-Therapy.jpg" alt="periods pain hot water bag, Heat-Therapy , " width="468" height="288" /> 3. Heat-Therapy[/caption]
<p style="text-align: justify;">This is the most common yet effective way to get rid of the menstrual cycle pain. Sit or lie down comfortably and put a hot water bottle over your abdominal area. You may also go for a hot bath before you go off to sleep as it soothes the cramps and makes you relaxed.</p>


[caption id="attachment_1063" align="alignnone" width="488"]<img class="wp-image-1063" src="http://homemadesolutions.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Woman-Walking-Away-Woman-Beach-Woman-Walking-Away-1149088.jpg" alt="Woman Walking Away Woman Beach Woman Walking Away" width="488" height="317" /> 4. walk[/caption]

